{"tid":1469544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問和理非係咪要全面退場？","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:26:30.000Z","uid":277621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"db307aeaa0e2f415ec6f47e0169e7094e0a35851","tid":1469544,"uid":277621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"永遠都係和理非要對勇武包容，唔指責，唔切割<br />\n但勇武有無尊重過和理非？<br />\n<br />\n85 後唔係講過同一場合唔好兩邊一齊做，混淆左活動性質？<br />\n<br />\n而家究竟機場活動目標係咩？<br />\n透過咩方式，想達到咩目的？<br />\n有無plan b? 有無界線？去到咩位要升級之類？<br />\n<br />\n唔係又一句前線決定就算，咁係不負責任<br />\n<br />\n連登係咪只可以有撐勇武的意見？"},{"pid":"5d7b30c21063656b0397771b823a1b1697553aac","tid":1469544,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:11:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda3b0f79bb33a6fe0ef8e960a7a0c3b1809686b","tid":1469544,"uid":150610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d946400e53b39107d94455707f7d3ee3b84579c","tid":1469544,"uid":67065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"罷工 又勇武<br />\n機場 又勇武<br />\n勇武做哂佢啦"},{"pid":"bf4786f768bbcb44e77a2c33daa4f13d0efe5f67","tid":1469544,"uid":277621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"村民無人記得要求雨，無人記得當初係為話比外來科學家知，呢度乾旱好需要水<br />\n<br />\n而家變左農民捉/火燒女巫嚟求雨"}]}